  title: The Hollow Desk
  briefText: The reporter's trail ends on an overnight records-floor sweep. Desk
    sergeant Inez Farrow says she never reopened the archive after sunset. Evidence
    from both departments ties her desk to the leak, Mira's broker network, and the
    vanished case routes.
